---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: The Lab Blog | Grooming Tips & Style Guides | Manor TX
description: Expert grooming advice, fade guides, and beard care tips from The Lab Barbershop in Manor, Texas. Updated regularly by our master barbers.
---

<section class="pt-40 pb-24 bg-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-4 tracking-tighter">LABORATORY <span class="text-lab-blue">LOG</span></h1>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">Expert grooming insight from our barbers in Manor, TX. Fades, beards, style, and everything in between.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-12">
            {% for post in collections.blogs | reverse %}
            <article class="glass p-8 md:p-12 rounded-sm transition-all hover:border-lab-blue/30 border-l-4 border-l-lab-blue/20">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-lab-blue uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">{{ post.date | postDate }}</span>
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold my-4 md:my-6 hover:text-lab-blue transition tracking-tight leading-tight"><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
                <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-6 md:mb-8 text-base md:text-lg">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4">
                    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-6 md:px-8 py-3 rounded-sm text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-lab-blue hover:text-white transition">Read Full Post</a>
                    <span class="text-zinc-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">By {{ post.data.author or "The Lab" }}</span>
                </div>
            </article>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
